[SN]TITLE[SN]
Elderly Gwbert man missing after going out on boat

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A search is under way for a 90-year-old man who is missing after going out on his boat off the Ceredigion coast.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Arthur Ray Taylor was last seen leaving to take his boat out to sea off Gwbert boat club at about 09:30 BST on Saturday.
Dyfed-Powys Police said Mr Taylor's boat has been found but he is still unaccounted for.
Police are coordinating a search of the area, working with the coastguard and RNLI.
Mr Taylor has been described as 5ft 4in tall, of slim build with grey hair and was wearing a navy jumper and a dark grey waterproof jacket.
Police have appealed for anyone who sees Mr Taylor or knows of his whereabouts to call 101.
